{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDAzNzE3Nzc4", "number": 2577, "title": "delegate `getMetadata()` to `R2DBCDatabaseContainerProvider`", "bodyText": "Apparently, R2DBC ConnectionFactories perform early validation of options, and it fails because the original options (when specified as r2dbc://mysql:///db) miss some required options like host/port/username/password.\nAfter talking to @mp911de, it seems that the checks will stay, so we need to workaround it somehow. I ended up with the delegation to R2DBCDatabaseContainerProvider, because these provides should know which options they add and which are required.\nContext:\nhttps://twitter.com/bsideup/status/1250093434817347586?s=20", "createdAt": "2020-04-15T12:03:06Z", "url": "https://github.com/testcontainers/testcontainers-java/pull/2577", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "3530e63d1d33801b4851acbe606d1282ebbd4298"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-04-19T09:11:36Z", "author": {"login": "bsideup"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 4, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcX20kbAH2gAyNDAzNzE3Nzc4OmZmYjJjNjYyNGVjMDUyMTc1MWE2ODM1MDIyOTkyYzFhYmQ2ZWQ0ZmQ=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcX4k1-AFqTM5MzgwMjkyNQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "ffb2c6624ec0521751a6835022992c1abd6ed4fd", "author": {"user": {"login": "bsideup", "name": "Sergei Egorov"}}, "url": "https://github.com/testcontainers/testcontainers-java/commit/ffb2c6624ec0521751a6835022992c1abd6ed4fd", "committedDate": "2020-04-15T11:58:38Z", "message": "delegate `getMetadata()` to `R2DBCDatabaseContainerProvider`"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3MzkzNzE0OTI2", "url": "https://github.com/testcontainers/testcontainers-java/pull/2577#pullrequestreview-393714926", "createdAt": "2020-04-15T12:13:56Z", "commit": {"oid": "ffb2c6624ec0521751a6835022992c1abd6ed4fd"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "com